# FaLocaleTranslationsInput and locale translations

## Reuse the shared element

Per-locale string field → **`FaLocaleTranslationsInput`** from **`src/components/elements/FaLocaleTranslationsInput/`** with **`v-model`** on **`I_faLocaleStringTranslations`**, **`current-language-code`**, required **`test-locator`**. **No** duplicate translate menus or fallback-warning wiring in feature folders.

**Project Settings today:** world **`displayNameTranslations`**, document template **`titleTranslations`**, template **`worldAppendixTranslations`**.

## Stored value contract

- Model: **`Partial<Record<T_faUserSettingsLanguageCode, string>>`** — **`types/I_faLocaleStringTranslations.ts`**
- Readonly main field shows **resolved** text for active UI language (preferred → **en-US** → sorted locales)
- Empty locale keys omitted on save/edit (trim + delete when blank)
- Domain max length: pass **`max-length`** prop; normalize at persist via domain **`createNormalize…`** helpers

## Resolver pipeline

| Piece | Role |
| --- | --- |
| **`src/scripts/localeTranslations/functions/resolveFaLocaleStringTranslation.ts`** | Display value + fallback language code |
| **`src/scripts/localeTranslations/faLocaleStringTranslations_manager.ts`** | Wired with **`FA_USER_SETTINGS_LANGUAGE_CODES`** |
| **`src/scripts/documentTemplates/faProjectDocumentTemplateTitle_manager.ts`** | Template title alias + max length |
| World display name / world appendix managers under **`src/scripts/projectWorlds/`**, **`src/scripts/documentTemplates/`** | Project Settings draft + snapshot normalize |

## Placement vs template draft (do not mix)

| Shape | **`worldAppendix`** | **`worldAppendixTranslations`** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Document template **draft** / snapshot item | — | yes |
| World template layout **placement** / he-tree node | yes (resolved string) | no |
| Layout **group** row | **`displayName: string`** only | — |

## Element API (short)

- **`inputMode`**: **`singleLine`** (default) \| **`multiline`**
- Click readonly field or translate button → locale menu; tooltip **only** on button
- **`#after`** fallback warning when resolved locale ≠ current UI language
- Test locators: **`{testLocator}`**, **`{testLocator}-translationsButton`**, **`{testLocator}-translationsMenu`**, **`{testLocator}-translationsInput-<code>`**, **`{testLocator}-fallbackWarning`**

## i18n and Storybook

- Strings: **`i18n/<locale>/components/elements/FaLocaleTranslationsInput/`**, keyed **`faLocaleTranslationsInput`** in **`index.ts`**
- Field labels stay in feature i18n (e.g. **`dialogs.projectSettings.fields.worldName.label`**)
- Storybook: **`_tests/*.stories.ts`**; extend **`.storybook-workspace/.storybook/mocks/externalFileLoader.ts`** when adding copy

## Two-level architecture

- **`src/scripts/localeTranslations/functions/`** — level-1 pure helpers only
- **`FaLocaleTranslationsInput/scripts/functions/createUseFaLocaleTranslationsInput.ts`** — level-1 composable factory (types from **`app/types/**`** only)
- **`faLocaleTranslationsInput_manager.ts`** — wiring-only **`useFaLocaleTranslationsInput`**

## Tests

- **`FaLocaleTranslationsInput/_tests/*.vitest.test.ts`** — resolve, fallback, menu emit, click-to-open
- **`src/scripts/localeTranslations/functions/_tests/`** — resolver + menu geometry
- Feature panels stub **`FaLocaleTranslationsInput`**; keep integration in element tests

